1
00:00:58,053 --> 00:01:01,029
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,029 --> 00:01:02,999
=Episode 12=

3
00:01:02,999 --> 00:01:07,021
(Let Me Blow It Out)

4
00:01:08,096 --> 00:01:11,296
(Training Ground, Gu Mansion)

5
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,640
Throw a punch.

6
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:15,319
How could I lay a hand on my wife?

7
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,680
Thank you.

8
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,400
Self-defense principle.

9
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:35,560
When your opponent is stronger,
learn to use their force against them.

10
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:41,040
If you can take one of my ten moves,

11
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,079
I will answer one of your questions

12
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:45,319
or do one thing for you.

13
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:47,120
I promise.

14
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,120
You won.

15
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:09,080
So, is there anything you want to ask
or anything you want me to do?

16
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,360
Let's stop here for today.

17
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:24,560
Think carefully about your question.

18
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,680
Come out.

19
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:45,439
Master, Gu Chaosheng has taken people
to the yamen to identify the remains.

20
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,560
Didn't we find out earlier
he hired an assassin?

21
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,520
So he must be the murderer, right?

22
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:51,919
Where's the jewelry
Yuluo sent to the yamen?

23
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,080
It's still there.

24
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,800
Go retrieve it.

25
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:02,280
Investigate the assassination
as soon as possible

26
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,360
and bring that jade pendant back.

27
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:08,800
Are our undercover agents
still at the yamen?

28
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,280
They are there.

29
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:14,560
But hasn't Gu Chaosheng already gone?
Should we still keep watching?

30
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,780
Of course.

31
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:19,800
The yamen will be very busy today.

32
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:42,240
What kind of grudge
did those bandits hold to go this far?

33
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,800
The most terrifying part is

34
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,680
that this wasn't done by bandits.

35
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,599
It was his own sibling.

36
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:11,120
Is there a problem with that?

37
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,319
No.

38
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,319
It's just the thought
of it being my little brother.

39
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,639
What are you talking about?

40
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:22,759
Isn't he safe in the mansion?

41
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:26,680
Besides, all of you Gus are blessed.

42
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,399
Gu?

43
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,279
Let's see if he deserves that surname.

44
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:39,839
Isn't Master Zhaoxi...?

45
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:45,480
It seems we need to reinvestigate
Master Zhaoxi's identity.

46
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:51,920
Next.

47
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,800
My son! My son!

48
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,199
This is terrifying.

49
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,639
Honey.

50
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,120
Let's go.

51
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,279
Such a tragedy. Dying so horribly.

52
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,879
Why are there so many people today?

53
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,079
Next.

54
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:37,639
Follow those three people.

55
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,019
Yes.

56
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,360
Sorry

57
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,759
for not collecting your remains in time.

58
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,879
Whether you are Gu Zhaoxi or not,

59
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,839
I won't let your death be in vain.

60
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,512
(Heaven)

61
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:04,079
Must you keep facing me
with this disguise?

62
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:14,040
Zhaoxi's mother
was the former Pavilion Master.

63
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:18,079
After you complete this task,
the two of you will marry.

64
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:23,759
Then I can pass
the Pavilion Master position to you.

65
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:49,187
(Imperial City)

66
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:53,319
Your Majesty, the scouts report
that the Crown Prince has...

67
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,944
(Emperor Yin Feng)

68
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,439
Your Majesty.

69
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,720
(Chief Eunuch He Zhongyi)
Someone, fetch the imperial physician!

70
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,000
Quickly!

71
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:02,920
Your Majesty.

72
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,399
I failed to protect Lianyi

73
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,600
and also Ci.

74
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,319
Now, even Zhou...

75
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:15,600
Your Majesty, please
take care of your health!

76
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,519
The Crown Prince's spirit

77
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:21,920
would find no peace
seeing you so heartbroken.

78
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,519
Your Majesty.

79
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,439
Who did this?

80
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:27,800
Your Majesty, please calm down
for your health!

81
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:31,639
Your Majesty, bandits outside the city
have been captured.

82
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:35,960
We will avenge the Crown Prince.

83
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,639
How dare you bite me?

84
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:47,399
Babe, if you weren't still useful to me,

85
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:52,279
I would've killed you.

86
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:05,200
Today, I'll spare your life.

87
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:16,200
Chief Li, the bandits outside the city
have been eliminated. Here's the file.

88
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,879
Present it.

89
00:09:23,759 --> 00:09:24,840
What are you afraid of?

90
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:34,240
(He's returned to the Gu family.)
Gu... Zhaoxi...

91
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:46,120
The person you asked me to investigate
has no connection with Prince Rui.

92
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,919
(Forsythia)
The Lantern Festival's investigation

93
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:55,360
shows the assassins colluded
with bandits outside the city.

94
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,639
The jade pendant was loot.

95
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,600
Now, Master Zhaoxi's name is cleared.

96
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,639
Another thing, just as you predicted,

97
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:07,240
Gu Zhaoxi is not Gu Jiang's son.

98
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:11,440
The former Pavilion Master Yun Sui
and Gu Jiang were once fellow disciples.

99
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:15,799
Though she married Gu Jiang, she was
already pregnant before the wedding.

100
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,879
She passed the next year
from an incurable old illness.

101
00:10:19,919 --> 00:10:22,240
This is what I've uncovered.

102
00:10:29,969 --> 00:10:36,992
(Gu Zhaoxi is not Gu Jiang's son.)

103
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,679
What are your thoughts on this?

104
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,159
So it seems

105
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:50,000
someone discovered Gu Zhaoxi
wasn't their blood brother

106
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,879
and then ruthlessly killed him.

107
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:55,600
Gu?

108
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,600
Let's see if he deserves that surname.

109
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:10,399
This is the former Pavilion Master
and the family head's privacy.

110
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,120
No word of it had been leaked for years.

111
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:16,960
How did Gu Chaosheng,
who wasn't involved, find out,

112
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:19,919
and how did you manage
to trace the clues back to it?

113
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,200
Are you saying...?

114
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:27,120
How deep does this web of shadows go?

115
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:29,360
The secret letter I received,

116
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:30,919
the secret Gu Chaosheng found,

117
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,000
and...

118
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:35,120
the family pharmacy.

119
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,279
They report fixed monthly losses
of medicinal herbs

120
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:40,639
which can form
a lethal poison when combined.

121
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:45,080
And by now, there's enough to kill.

122
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,519
Master.

123
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:54,879
The mastermind's ambitions
extend beyond the Xuanji Pavilion.

124
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:58,080
I'm afraid their target
is the entire Gu family.

125
00:12:10,039 --> 00:12:11,399
Was I too heavy-handed?

126
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:15,159
No, something just got in my eye.

127
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,440
Let me blow it out.

128
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,399
Better now?

129
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,480
Have you decided
what you'd like to ask me?

130
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,159
Not yet.

131
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,919
Take your time.

132
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,399
Just tell me when you've decided.

133
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:34,740
Dear.

134
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,679
Master.

135
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:38,759
What is it?

136
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:43,200
The rouge shop in the north quarter says
the shade you requested has arrived.

137
00:13:46,679 --> 00:13:47,320
Understood.

138
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,440
I'll be right back.

139
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:52,320
Summon Xuan Qing if anything arises.

140
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:20,200
(Third courtyard on West Street.
Come immediately.)

141
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:23,799
(There's no rouge shop there.)

142
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:27,480
(Seems it's time for him to learn
their coded messages.)

143
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:34,840
Take your time.

144
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:38,559
Wanniang, I haven't seen you for days.

145
00:14:38,679 --> 00:14:40,519
Fresh fruit. Care to look?

146
00:14:40,639 --> 00:14:41,600
Let me look.

147
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:47,279
I've bought too much today.
I can't carry it all.

148
00:14:47,399 --> 00:14:48,519
I'll return tomorrow to buy.

149
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:50,759
Why did you buy so many things?

150
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,399
You're hosting guests today?

151
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,080
Yeah.

152
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:56,960
Take care.

153
00:15:08,159 --> 00:15:12,200
Such a hurried guest.
I haven't even prepared the table yet.

154
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,879
Leng Yan lacks care in the underworld.

155
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:17,120
Let me send you down to cook for him.

156
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,160
You know martial arts.
You're not Wanniang!

157
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,320
But what does that matter?

158
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,960
You think with a basket, you can win?

159
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:30,200
You violence-obsessed folk
always carry blades.

160
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:31,759
What's the use?

161
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:37,759
Blades? I can find one anytime.

162
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:53,320
Take him away. Find out who he serves.

163
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:54,320
- Yes.
- Yes.

164
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,519
(Rouge.)

165
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:08,279
Master, what took you so long?

166
00:18:09,119 --> 00:18:13,200
May I know how I've offended you?

167
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:18,160
(Zuixian Building's owner)
Many in the capital are seeking you.

168
00:18:18,759 --> 00:18:21,920
You announced your hometown return,
but actually, you're hiding here?

169
00:18:23,119 --> 00:18:26,920
You surely know why they pursue you?

170
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,680
I genuinely don't.

171
00:18:31,279 --> 00:18:34,880
Then I'll ask Physician Qin.

172
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:37,160
Where is he? What have you done to him?

173
00:18:39,519 --> 00:18:40,720
He's perfectly fine.

174
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:43,480
But if your answers disappoint me...

175
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:46,400
How do I know this isn't a bluff?

176
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,599
You know who're hunting you, right?

177
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:53,960
What will happen if they capture you?

178
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,880
Cooperate fully,

179
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:58,359
and I guarantee your safety.

180
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,680
Safety?

181
00:19:01,119 --> 00:19:03,799
If anyone could protect us,

182
00:19:03,839 --> 00:19:05,480
that matter from 19 years ago...

183
00:20:32,816 --> 00:20:37,879
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

184
00:20:38,416 --> 00:20:43,737
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

185
00:20:44,304 --> 00:20:50,932
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

186
00:20:50,932 --> 00:20:55,696
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

187
00:20:55,696 --> 00:20:58,032
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

188
00:20:58,032 --> 00:21:04,732
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

189
00:21:04,732 --> 00:21:11,504
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

190
00:21:11,504 --> 00:21:18,640
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

191
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:23,024
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

192
00:21:23,024 --> 00:21:25,648
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

193
00:21:25,648 --> 00:21:32,282
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

194
00:21:32,282 --> 00:21:38,832
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

195
00:21:38,832 --> 00:21:45,956
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

196
00:21:46,046 --> 00:21:50,416
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

197
00:21:50,416 --> 00:21:53,124
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

198
00:21:53,124 --> 00:21:59,024
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

199
00:21:59,664 --> 00:22:05,652
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
